data.description: Welcome to this exquisite luxury home, nearly 4000 sq ft of living space on a sprawling one-acre lot within the highly esteemed North Side Dayton Ridge Estates. Crafted with uncompromising quality and precision, this home boasts superior 2 x 6 construction, ensuring not only enduring resilience but also enhanced energy efficiency. The property welcomes you with an expansive 3-car garage and an enchanting 900 sq ft covered stamped concrete patio, with a gourmet outdoor kitchen, setting the stage for grand soirees and lavish entertaining.  Step inside and be enveloped by the sophisticated allure of hardwood floors, the warm embrace of a wood-burning fireplace, and soaring 9' ceilings, creating an inviting ambiance. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's reverie, featuring granite countertops, cherry cabinetry, a grand center island with a secondary sink, and a spacious walk-in pantry, while the adjacent formal dining room promises elegant culinary gatherings.  Further enchantment awaits with a four-season sunroom, a convenient first-floor bedroom and bath, a private office, and a generous laundry area. Ascend to the master suite, a haven of tranquility boasting a whirlpool tub, a separate shower, dual vanities, and an expansive walk-in closet, complete with additional storage above the garage. The third bedroom boasts custom designed built-in beds/desks. This exceptional residence extends its allure with an unfinished basement, pre-plumbed for an additional bathroom, graced by egress windows and lofty 10' ceilings, offering endless possibilities for custom luxury enhancements.   This exquisite property combines elegance, functionality, and the serenity of Dayton Ridge Estates. Don't miss the opportunity to call this your forever home. Schedule a viewing today to experience luxury living at its finest.
